write a program to check anagram in array 
problem Statement:
Given a String of different words, group all the anagrams together.
 
Input: arr[] = ["cat", "god", "act", "dog", "tac", "abb", "aac"]
Output: [[“act”, “cat”, “tac”], [“god”, “dog”], ["abb"], ["aac"]]
 
Explanation: 
There are 2 groups of anagrams  “act”, “cat”, “tac” make group 1. “god”, “dog” make group 2. Then there are no anagrams for "aac" and "abb".


